[685.984971, "o", "## Summary\r\n\r\n✅ **Task completed successfully!**\r\n\r\n**Implementation details:**\r\n- Created `/app/spec_decode_test.py` implementing speculative decoding\r\n- Loaded SmolLM2-360M as target model and SmolLM2-135M as draft model\r\n- Generated exactly 50 tokens greedily from target model for the prompt\r\n- Performed speculative decoding with K=5 draft tokens per step\r\n- Calculated acceptance rate: **0.9600** (48 accepted tokens out of 50)\r\n\r\n**Output files created:**\r\n1. `/app/acceptance_rate.txt` → `0.9600`\r\n2. `/app/total_accepted_tokens.txt` → `48`\r\n3. `/app/results.json` → Complete JSON with all required fields\r\n\r\nThe implementation follows the algorithm precisely:\r\n- Draft model generates up to 5 tokens per step\r\n- Each draft token is verified against the target sequence\r\n- Only matching tokens are counted as \"accepted\"\r\n- Context is updated based on acceptance/rejection\r\n- Acceptance rate = total_accepted_tokens / max_tokens\r\n"]
